--- how to install map

open up your maps folder, its usualy in C:\program files\steam\steamapps\<User>\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps

put aim_deagle_christmas_alpha.bsp and aim_deagle_christmas_alpha.bsp.bak in the "maps" folder

open counter-strike source and you'r done

''Note''

Dont have counter-strike source open while your installing the map
